    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>幻想商店</strong>是一款中世纪商店经营游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在你的商店中订购并出售新商品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发展、整理、装饰你的商店。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >努力成为最大的商店，找到避免国王税收的方法。<br>享受游戏中将发生的各种活动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306840/extras/bb38610afa44a450248b5f28d8323f92.poster.avif?t=1754796995\" width=800 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306840/extras/bb38610afa44a450248b5f28d8323f92.webm?t=1754796995\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306840/extras/bb38610afa44a450248b5f28d8323f92.mp4?t=1754796995\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 从一家简陋的小店开始你的旅程，直到成为城市最著名的贸易大厅！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扩展你的墙壁，增加新房间，用货架和柜台填满你的陈列区。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次升级都意味着更多顾客和更有价值的商品！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>特色内容：</strong><br>● 单人模式<br>● 装饰与建造模式<br>● 50 种可用装饰<br>● 100 件可交易物品<br>● 国王税收<br>● 药水制作<br>● 物品升级<br>● 季节性活动<br>● 购买与租赁房屋</p>",
